{"tid":315913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[沉船毒男]同大陸妹傾完計番唔到轉頭","createTime":"2017-07-10T11:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T10:44:35.000Z","uid":87515,"like":6,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a381f55249b1f383a1b51e7eeb436430655a76b","tid":315913,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"話說今日返lecture去canteen食早餐，無啦啦有堆大陸學生團入哂黎，霸住幾張長枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正當我一邊將碗火腿通搬去遙遠既風景位，一邊慨歎學生canteen都俾大陸佬侵佔既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地突然散開，有兩個學生妹過咗黎我張枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當我以為佢地黎揾我做濕勁問卷，佢地問我可唔可以坐低，咁我求其話是但啦，等陣扮聽電話走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個兩個大陸妹睇個樣都幾標致，唔會話太鄉下村姑，仲有少少清純，衫都係高中個Ｄ死人PE衫，只不過差條紅領巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然話係高中，但身材已經直達C,甚至D既級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.people.com.cn/mediafile/pic/20130522/78/5086907759562928450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com.cn%2Fmediafile%2Fpic%2F20130522%2F78%2F5086907759562928450.jpg&h=48241ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.fei123.com/upload/2016/02/02/326e9aad-0467-48ab-bd0c-4b6ec94cd622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fei123.com%2Fupload%2F2016%2F02%2F02%2F326e9aad-0467-48ab-bd0c-4b6ec94cd622.jpg&h=92a84eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貼番幅圖保護阿媽<br />\n<br />\n一開始佢地問我關於升學既野，問入呢間大學難唔難，大學生活點。由於小弟自中學已經幾年無講過普通話，講出黎甩甩cut cut咁，不過佢地都聽得明<br />\n<br />\n佢地以為香港打工仲係好輕鬆，我同佢地講其實係香港揾食唔係咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地同一般中學雞一樣，以為要落操場早會上堂，當我話八點半堂可以八點三先起身，佢地兩個即刻呆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你眼望我眼，個樣幾cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,有時我講個笑話氹下佢地 ，佢地會掩住個嘴笑，身為青頭既我受不住了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gaoxiao.g-smart.cn/uploads/allimg/160826/1_0R601020V3b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaoxiao.g-smart.cn%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F160826%2F1_0R601020V3b.gif&h=e19ce3a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i3.sinaimg.cn/ent/m/p/2011-09-25/U3593P28T3D3426689F346DT20110925201515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fm%2Fp%2F2011-09-25%2FU3593P28T3D3426689F346DT20110925201515.jpg&h=0fb20f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到最後，有個大陸miss黎叫我同佢地影合照，我夾係佢地中間，手肘唔小心hi到佢地個波，好軟好有彈力呀，佢地影完就走咗，跟住我先醒起未問佢地拎v7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲諗住可以日後聯絡下<br />\n<br />\n而家灰到連lecture都唔想上，有無巴打可以幫我拉埋命運既紅線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:非5毛，非FF"},{"pid":"5ec0825bde48a96f9d902ee52082ccd4d41f0127","tid":315913,"uid":50328,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15df3cf1a796a7cccb7bdb1fddfd2e0c4d9ff464","tid":315913,"uid":87515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都見到佢地兩個,帶左番屋企食左,真係番唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊，上黎接番走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bd03b38d5ef30cf2faf5f9bfcca1ed6743e02f","tid":315913,"uid":50328,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0ab47ef473bee6508b4effba5312a95106aa765","tid":315913,"uid":20429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"hi撚完波邊重想拎電話？搏拉吖"},{"pid":"1b87e97573f4a27fd9eaff3657e1c3cd5384b773","tid":315913,"uid":69753,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思吖<br />\n但係關我撚事呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8130ca631cdb4cb12b29bf897af79bc052a7fd5","tid":315913,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi撚完波邊重想拎電話？搏拉吖</blockquote><br />\n青頭毒男想識下女仔啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔通幾十歲等人揾我埋單咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62736ad8284521722116102f735481e9157c6412","tid":315913,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思吖<br />\n但係關我撚事呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又上連登"},{"pid":"4b2ab49bba69617f2ad8ab23d8fb675dfa9a83e4","tid":315913,"uid":125357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"支那妓女"},{"pid":"c444c968570ab411cf8ce5de866ecbaaa3abfc70","tid":315913,"uid":87515,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"有得比你揀，你會揀無波臭西性格港女，定係大波嬌聲嬌氣大陸妹？"},{"pid":"27f72ddcca35ecf4d7677e1fe545db6cf26ac50a","tid":315913,"uid":5253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"大波嬌聲嬌氣香港妹"},{"pid":"138d0f77d97550a4f52fb91c4ab2a22666a08890","tid":315913,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大波嬌聲嬌氣香港妹</blockquote><br />\n邊有咁易遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928fd19855fc03f0f1d901063f1bb92091657d3f","tid":315913,"uid":33767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"沉唔係問題<br />\n但玩完俾D手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好娶返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7c471c56a32e5c0d0a20949f9585c7a4005eb2",